              <li>✓ <strong>Sealed pit installation</strong> - Prevents odors, moisture, and radon infiltration</li>
              <li>✓ <strong>24/7 emergency replacement</strong> - Same-day service when your pump fails</li>
              <li>✓ <strong>Annual maintenance programs</strong> - Preventive care to avoid emergency situations</li>
              <li>✓ <strong>Integration with waterproofing</strong> - Complete basement water management systems</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="installation-includes">
